snippet.title: Chico and the Magic Orchards (Trailer 2)
snippet.description:
Chico and the Magic Orchards is coming soon to PC, Mac, and Linux.
Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1921550/Chico_and_the_Magic_Orchards/

When Chico the chipmunk stumbles into a portal in the forest, he’s transported to a magical world where he finds giant walnuts galore. It's getting them home that's the tricky part! 

Solve puzzles and challenges across a variety of worlds, grow your stash of giant walnuts, beat intimidating bosses, and help Chico get back to his forest!
